Launch centos7 ec2-instance (Nagios is not support on amazon linux)
cd /opt 
wget http://assets.nagios.com/downloads/nagiosxi/xi-latest.tar.gz  (Step1. Download software)
tar -xzf xi-latest.tar.gz   (untar file)
cd nagiosxi/
./fullinstall  (Run Install script)
http://192.168.72.133/nagiosxi/   (Access UI using public IP)

Nagios Agent:
cd /tmp
wget https://assets.nagios.com/downloads/nagiosxi/agents/linux-nrpe-agent.tar.gz
tar -xzf xi-latest.tar.gz  (Untar file)
./fullinstall   (Run script)
Sudo service start ixnetd